    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "michael@revenuecs.com",
        "toEmail": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "You're live. The system is dialing.",
        "emailFormat": "html",
        "message": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f4f4f5;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;\">\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:40px 20px;\">\n<table width=\"560\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\">\n<tr><td style=\"background:#0f0f0f;padding:32px 40px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#86efac;text-transform:uppercase;\">RevenueCS \u2014 System Live</p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;line-height:1.3;\">You're live. The system is dialing.</h1>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:36px 40px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;\">Hey {{ $json.businessName }} team,</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 20px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;\">This is the moment everything's been building toward. Your <strong>{{ $json.systemType }}</strong> system is fully configured, tested, and live. As of right now the system is actively working your contact list \u2014 reaching out, qualifying, and booking appointments automatically, around the clock.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 28px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;\">Your ROI dashboard is live and tracking every interaction in real time. This is your command center \u2014 check it any time to see exactly what the system is doing for your business:</p>\n  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:32px;\"><tr><td style=\"background:#6366f1;border-radius:8px;\">\n    <a href=\"{{ $json.roiDashboardUrl }}\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;\">Open Your ROI Dashboard &#8594;</a>\n  </td></tr></table>\n  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#f9fafb;border-radius:8px;width:100%;margin-bottom:28px;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:20px 24px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;\">What to expect in the first 7 days</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\">&#128222; <strong>Days 1\u20132:</strong> System warms up \u2014 call volume starts lower while we verify connect rates</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\">&#128200; <strong>Days 3\u20135:</strong> Volume increases, first bookings typically start coming in</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 8px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\">&#9989; <strong>Days 5\u20137:</strong> Full throughput \u2014 the system is running at full capacity</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;\">If the first day looks quiet, that's normal. Warmup is intentional \u2014 we'd rather start clean than burn your list on day one.</p>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#f9fafb;border-radius:8px;width:100%;margin-bottom:28px;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:20px 24px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;\">Numbers to watch</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\"><strong>Call connect rate</strong> \u2014 healthy target is above 30%</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\"><strong>Demo book rate</strong> \u2014 we aim for 8\u201315% of connected calls booking</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\"><strong>No-show rate</strong> \u2014 we work to keep this below 25%</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:10px 0 0;font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;\">If you see anything look off in the first week, reply to this email immediately. We review numbers daily and make script and targeting adjustments before they become real problems.</p>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;\">You'll get a weekly performance report every Monday morning. We're watching the system every day \u2014 if anything needs tuning, we're on it before you have to ask.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#374151;\">Let's get those bookings in.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#374151;\">\u2014 Michael</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"background:#f9fafb;padding:20px 40px;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;\">Michael \u2014 RevenueCS &nbsp;&#183;&nbsp; michael@revenuecs.com</p>\n</td></tr>\n</table></td></tr></table></body></html>",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "email-golive-client",
      "name": "Email - Go-Live to Client",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.emailSend",
      "typeVersion": 2.1,
      "position": [
        680,
        100
      ],
      "credentials": {
        "smtp": {
          "id": "LViY7g19KwnPtnEG",
          "name": "SMTP account 2"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "michael@revenuecs.com",
        "toEmail": "michael@revenuecs.com",
        "subject": "&#128640; Client Live \u2014 {{ $json.businessName }} | {{ $json.systemType }}",
        "emailFormat": "html",
        "message": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f4f4f5;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;\">\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:32px 20px;\">\n<table width=\"540\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#ffffff;border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);\">\n<tr><td style=\"background:#0c4a6e;padding:24px 32px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;color:#7dd3fc;text-transform:uppercase;\">Client Live \u2014 RevenueCS</p>\n  <h2 style=\"margin:6px 0 0;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;\">&#128640; {{ $json.businessName }} is live.</h2>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:28px 32px;\">\n  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#f8fafc;border-radius:8px;width:100%;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:16px 20px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;color:#6b7280;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;\">Client Info</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\"><strong>Business:</strong> {{ $json.businessName }}</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\"><strong>Email:</strong> {{ $json.email }}</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\"><strong>System:</strong> {{ $json.systemType }}</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\"><strong>MRR:</strong> ${{ $json.monthlyRetainer }}/mo</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#6b7280;\"><strong>ROI Dashboard:</strong> <a href=\"{{ $json.roiDashboardUrl }}\" style=\"color:#6366f1;\">open dashboard</a></p>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#e0f2fe;border:1px solid #7dd3fc;border-radius:8px;width:100%;margin-bottom:20px;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:14px 20px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#0c4a6e;\">Monitoring checklist</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:13px;color:#0c4a6e;\">&#9744; Review connect rate after Day 2 (target: &gt;30%)</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:13px;color:#0c4a6e;\">&#9744; Check first booking came in by Day 5</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 4px;font-size:13px;color:#0c4a6e;\">&#9744; Weekly ROI report will begin next Monday automatically</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#0c4a6e;\">&#9744; Flag any anomalies \u2014 no-show spike, low connect rate \u2014 before Day 7</p>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;\">Go-live email sent to client. Weekly ROI reports will start automatically this Monday.</p>\n</td></tr>\n</table></td></tr></table></body></html>",
        "options": {}
      },
