    {
      "parameters": {
        "fromEmail": "michael@revenuecs.com",
        "toEmail": "={{ $json.email }}",
        "subject": "This week's numbers are in \u2014 {{ $json.businessName }}",
        "emailFormat": "html",
        "message": "<!DOCTYPE html><html><body style=\"margin:0;padding:0;background:#f4f4f5;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',sans-serif;\">\n<table width=\"100%\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tr><td align=\"center\" style=\"padding:40px 20px;\">\n<table width=\"560\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#ffffff;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);\">\n<tr><td style=\"background:#0f0f0f;padding:32px 40px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;color:#a5b4fc;text-transform:uppercase;\">RevenueCS \u2014 Weekly Report</p>\n  <h1 style=\"margin:8px 0 0;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;color:#ffffff;line-height:1.3;\">This week's numbers are in.</h1>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"padding:36px 40px;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 20px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;\">Hey {{ $json.businessName }} team,</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 24px;font-size:15px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;\">Your weekly performance summary is ready. Below you'll find this week's call volume, connect rate, appointments booked, and the total estimated revenue your system generated \u2014 all broken down so you can see exactly where the numbers are coming from.</p>\n  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin-bottom:32px;\"><tr><td style=\"background:#6366f1;border-radius:8px;\">\n    <a href=\"{{ $json.roiDashboardUrl }}\" style=\"display:inline-block;padding:14px 32px;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;\">View This Week's Full Report &#8594;</a>\n  </td></tr></table>\n  <table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"background:#f9fafb;border-radius:8px;width:100%;margin-bottom:28px;\">\n    <tr><td style=\"padding:20px 24px;\">\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 12px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;color:#6b7280;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.08em;\">What's in your report</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\">\u2022 <strong>Total calls made</strong> this week vs. last week</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\">\u2022 <strong>Connect rate</strong> \u2014 how often the system reached a live person</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0 0 6px;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\">\u2022 <strong>Appointments booked</strong> \u2014 the number that matters most</p>\n      <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#111827;\">\u2022 <strong>Estimated revenue generated</strong> based on your average deal value</p>\n    </td></tr>\n  </table>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-size:14px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;\">We review these numbers every single week on our end too. If we see anything off \u2014 a dip in connect rate, lower book rate, higher no-shows \u2014 we make adjustments without you having to ask. That's the job.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0 0 16px;font-size:14px;color:#374151;line-height:1.6;\">Something look wrong or confusing in the data? Reply to this email and I'll get back to you same day.</p>\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:14px;color:#374151;\">\u2014 Michael</p>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td style=\"background:#f9fafb;padding:20px 40px;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;\">\n  <p style=\"margin:0;font-size:13px;color:#9ca3af;\">Michael \u2014 RevenueCS &nbsp;&#183;&nbsp; michael@revenuecs.com</p>\n</td></tr>\n</table></td></tr></table></body></html>",
        "options": {}
